akness in the", "bbox": [143.7, 1075.0, 1093.6, 1095.8]}, {"text": "construction and the North American auto service markets, and restructuring costs.", "bbox": [143.7, 1100.0, 851.1, 1120.8]}, {"text": "Material Handling revenue decreased 1% while earnings decreased 5% when compared to the prior year.", "bbox": [185.4, 1137.6, 1093.8, 1158.4]}, {"text": "Revenue and earnings growth in the industrial winch business was more than offset by softness in the infrastructure,", "bbox": [143.7, 1162.5, 1093.4, 1183.3]}, {"text": "industrial automation and automotive markets. In addition, the platform incurred additional expenses related to its", "bbox": [143.7, 1187.5, 1093.8, 1208.4]}, {"text": "ongoing cost reduction and integration activities.", "bbox": [143.7, 1212.6, 559.0, 1233.4]}, {"text": "Mobile Equipment revenue and earnings increased 5% and 2%, respectively, over the prior year. The revenue", "bbox": [185.4, 1250.0, 1093.5, 1270.8]}, {"text": "increase was primarily due to core business growth as the platform continued to experience strength in the", "bbox": [143.7, 1275.0, 1093.6, 1295.9]}, {"text": "aerospace, military and solid waste management markets. Softness in the automotive service and bulk transport end", "bbox": [143.7, 1300.1, 1093.7, 1320.9]}, {"text": "markets partially offset the increases experienced in other markets.", "bbox": [143.7, 1325.0, 713.8, 1345.8]}, {"text": "25", "bbox": [608.4, 1515.3, 629.2, 1536.1]}]}